</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 RECALLING ROMERO: Emil Sitka of Camarillo played the foil in countless 
episodes of "The Three Stooges."But when he wasn't taking a pie in the face, 
Sitka worked with more serious actors, including Cesar Romero, who died 
Saturday. . . . "He loved being a star," said Sitka, who worked with Romero and 
Betty Grable on "The Beautiful Blonde From Bashful Bend" in 1949. "He really 
liked the party circuit.". . . At 78, Sitka doesn't party much himself anymore, 
but he may attend a Stooge-lovers convention in Philadelphia this summer. "I 
still get fan mail." Gary Gorman 
</P>
</TEXT>
