</P>
<P>
 5. J.C. Penney Co. Inc. 
</P>
<P>
 * Based: Dallas 
</P>
<P>
 * Subsidiaries: J.C. Penney department stores, Thrift-Treasury Drug, Units 
clothing stores. 
</P>
<P>
 6. May Department Stores Co. 
</P>
<P>
