first-team offense. Brethren Christian tackle Darryl Jones was named to the 
small schools' first-team offense. Calvary Chapel lineman Dan Sundquist and 
Brethren Christian defensive back Reggie Davis were named first-team defense. 
Brethren Christian running back/linebacker Keith Washington was named to the 
multi-purpose team. 
