<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD:; THE MENENDEZ TRIAL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Times erroneously reported Dec. 10 that Jill Lansing, attorney for Lyle 
Menendez, burst into tears at the conclusion of her closing argument in the 
Menendez brothers' murder trial. She did not burst into tears, and she 
maintained professional composure throughout her argument. 
</P>
